import pymysql
from pyecharts import options as opts
from pyecharts.commons.utils import JsCode
from pyecharts.charts import Bar, Map, Grid, Timeline

#定义DB数据库类，封装在读取修改开始和结束时都需要进行连接（打开），断开（关闭）等固定操作，参考：https://www.runoob.com/python3/python3-mysql.html
class DB():
    def __init__(self, host='localhost', port=3306, db='g9', user='root', passwd='pythonclass', charset='utf8'):
        # 建立连接 
        self.conn = pymysql.connect(host=host, port=port, db=db, user=user, passwd=passwd, charset=charset)
        # 创建游标，操作设置为字典类型        
        #self.cur = self.conn.cursor(cursor = pymysql.cursors.DictCursor)
        self.cur = self.conn.cursor()

    def __enter__(self):
        # 返回游标        
        return self.cur

    def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb):
        # 提交数据库并执行        
        self.conn.commit()
        # 关闭游标        
        self.cur.close()
        # 关闭数据库连接        
        self.conn.close()

timeline = Timeline()
     
with DB() as db:
    for year in range(2011,2021):
        data = []
        data_x = []
        data_y = []
        
        #从数据库读取数据
        db.execute("SELECT data,shengfen FROM meiwang WHERE year = %s ORDER BY data*1 DESC LIMIT 10", year)
        for data0 in db:
            data.append([data0[1], data0[0]])
            data_x.append(data0[1])
            data_y.append(data0[0])   
        data_x.reverse()
        data_y.reverse()
        
        #绘制Top10柱状图
        d_bar = (
            Bar()
            .add_xaxis(data_x)
            .add_yaxis(series_name="每万人拥有卫生技术人员数", y_axis=data_y)
            .set_series_opts(label_opts=opts.LabelOpts(position="right"))
            .reversal_axis()  #翻转坐标轴
            .set_global_opts(
                title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title=str(year)+'年'),
                xaxis_opts=opts.AxisOpts(max_='160'), 
                visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(dimension=0,min_=50,max_=160,pos_left="right")
            )
        )
        
        #绘制地图，标注Top10
        d_map = (
            Map()
            .add(series_name="每万人拥有卫生技术人员数", data_pair=data, maptype="china",zoom = 1)
            .set_global_opts(
                title_opts=opts.TitleOpts(title=str(year)+'年'),
                visualmap_opts=opts.VisualMapOpts(dimension=0,min_=50,max_=160,pos_left="right")
            )
        )
        
        #合成柱状图与地图
        grid = (
            Grid()
            .add(d_bar, grid_opts=opts.GridOpts(pos_right="68%",pos_top="48%"))
            .add(d_map, grid_opts=opts.GridOpts())
        )
        
        #将图添加到时间线中
        timeline.add(grid, "{}年".format(year))    

#输出并展示
timeline.render("meiwang.html")
timeline.render_notebook()

%matplotlib inline
import pymysql
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from matplotlib.font_manager import FontProperties

font = FontProperties(fname="SimHei.ttf", size=28)

#定义DB数据库类，封装在读取修改开始和结束时都需要进行连接（打开），断开（关闭）等固定操作，参考：https://www.runoob.com/python3/python3-mysql.html
class DB():
    def __init__(self, host='localhost', port=3306, db='g9', user='root', passwd='pythonclass', charset='utf8'):
        # 建立连接 
        self.conn = pymysql.connect(host=host, port=port, db=db, user=user, passwd=passwd, charset=charset)
        # 创建游标，操作设置为字典类型        
        #self.cur = self.conn.cursor(cursor = pymysql.cursors.DictCursor)
        self.cur = self.conn.cursor()

    def __enter__(self):
        # 返回游标        
        return self.cur

    def __exit__(self, exc_type, exc_val, exc_tb):
        # 提交数据库并执行        
        self.conn.commit()
        # 关闭游标        
        self.cur.close()
        # 关闭数据库连接        
        self.conn.close()          

with DB() as db:
    plt.figure(figsize=(50, 200), dpi=150)
    plt.suptitle("每万人拥有卫生技术人员数与地区GDP", fontsize=48, fontproperties=font)
    for year in range(2011,2021):
        data = [] 
        data_x = [] 
        data_y = [] 
        db.execute("SELECT meiwang.data, gdp.data, meiwang.shengfen FROM meiwang, gdp WHERE meiwang.year = %s AND gdp.year = %s AND meiwang.shengfen = gdp.shengfen ORDER BY gdp.data*1", [year, year])
        for data0 in db:
            data.append([data0[1], data0[0]])
            data_x.append(float(data0[1]))
            data_y.append(int(data0[0]))
 
        plt.subplot(10, 1, year-2010)
        plt.scatter(data_x, data_y, c='red')
        plt.title(str(year)+"年", fontsize=32, fontproperties=font)
        plt.xlabel("地区GDP", fontproperties=font)
        plt.ylabel("每万人拥有卫生技术人员数", fontproperties=font)
    
    plt.savefig("temp.png")
    plt.show()
